reviewText:
My 6 year old and 4 year old absolutely loved all of these movies.  They kept watching them multiple times.  I think they have their favorites of the #2 and #4 movie, but I liked #1 & #2 because they had Eddie Murphy in them.  His humor is priceless regardless if he is acting for a family movie like these or for a more adult (R) rated move which these are not.
This is a great way to purchase all 4 movies and keep them together also.  They are in two hard plastic DVD holders, one with #'s 1 & 2 and the other with #'s 3 & 4.  The two plastic DVD holders are in the cardboard sleeve you see in the picture.

I bought this for my sister as a gift.  She really likes animals.  I had seen the first movie with Eddie and thought is was pretty funny.  However I haven't watched the other movies that are included.  So I don't know how good they are.

I got this one because it was a great deal for 4 movies.  To buy them individually would have been much more.
Product played great and they were funny and very entertaining. Good clean, funny and very entertaining. An animal lovers delight.
We ought this for my grandson. He really likes Dr. Doolittle and this was a perfect stocking stuffer for Christmas.
I enjoyed all 4 movies. If I like a movie, I watch it over and over. These movies are that type of movie for me.
Grew up watching these movies, still an old favourite,and the packaging is of such great quality! The movie's are an awesome buy if you want some family fun!

Was a little disappointed as I thought 4 movies would come in 4 different sleeves but the movies were just fine and I loved them.  I guess I need to read better when I read the discriptions  ;o)  I am pleased with the speedy shipment and the movies themselves.
Great
Loved the series

When there is a 4 pack that you can watch. Just because Eddie is only in the 1st 2 movies does not make the last ones bad.

I was always a fan of Eddy Murphy.  when Dr. Dolittle came out, I really enjoyed this movie over and over.  this box set has the first movie which is great. it also has the second which was okay.  this set also includes two movies staring the daughter. which is alright but if your wanting the just the Eddy Murphy then you might want to pass on this box set. I personally don't mind so to each there own.
Item was damaged. Money was returned, but we still have a Dr. Dolittle 4 pack that is actually a 3 pack and its a little annoying.

I don't really care about 3 & 4. I liked 1 and 2 a lot and getting the 4 pack was cheaper than getting them separately.

Not much else to say here.

The movie itself is about a man who can talk to animals and denies his special talent in the first one, but learns to embrace it as time goes on.

I don't think it needed a PG-13 rating...but parents should watch it first just to be safe... I don't know how strict some of you guys are.
My son has loved Dr Dolittle movies since he was young. We updated from VHS to DVD's. This was the first time seeing #3 and #4. Enjoyed them just as well.
Perfect condition! Kids loved these movies! I had never seen the others, only number 1. What a riot, my kids laugh so hard every time we watch them.
This is a great series - enjoyed every minute. Eddie Murphy is a great comic, every movie i have with him in it is great.
